		<RichText x="66" y="1008" width="436" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">晶寒加护：<span color="#99ffff">56冻</span><span>盾，击破后霜落立即死亡，可伤害转化。该状态下，抗打断0，免疫风场力。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊使徒%B7霜落.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1391" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊使徒%B7霜落.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1392" y="394">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊使徒%B7霜落.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1392" y="617">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊使徒%B7霜落.assets/Image_17.png')" x="719" y="841">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，霜落冲击过来划一刀，造成<span color="#99ffff">70%</span><span>伤害，若已开盾，则另增加一段翻卷戳地，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">86%</span><span>伤害。可附魔</span><span color="#7fffff">「渊冰」</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，霜落用转身扔出一根黯色的冰锥，造成<span color="#99ffff">78%</span><span>伤害，</span><span color="#ffb299">必定</span><span>附魔</span><span color="#7fffff">「渊冰」</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="703" width="410" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">霜落腾空，迅速朝地面发射2批锥冰刀片，第一批4个第二批5个，每个造成<span color="#99ffff">66%,33%</span><span>伤害。</span><span color="#ffb299">必定</span><span>附魔</span><span color="#7fffff">「渊冰」</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="441" height="229" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">未被护盾有效庇护的玩家被附魔有<span color="#7fffff">「渊冰」</span><span>的攻击命中时，首次扣除</span><span color="#99ffe5">50体力</span><span>，3s内若再次命中则扣除</span><span color="#99ffe5">20体力</span><span>。<br/>每一次进行</span><span color="#99ffff">附魔</span><span>的攻击前，都有20%(没盾)/27%(开盾)概率获得附魔，成功附魔后清零；当施放</span><span color="#44ebf2">「渊冰晶片」</span><span>后，下一次获得附魔的概率下降61%，若为施放</span><span color="#44ebf2">「肆锋舞冽」</span><span>后，则下次必无附魔。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2686a2" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2686a2">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="429" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">霜落使用冰刀进行2至4段普通攻击，全4段依次造成<span color="#99ffff">66%,55%,55%,75%</span><span>伤害。<br/>总计有3种施放方式：<br/>23段(</span><span color="#9fe4ff">阶段1-3</span><span>)，前3(</span><span color="#9fe4ff">阶段1-2</span><span>)，<br/>全4(</span><span color="#9fe4ff">阶段2-3</span><span>)。可附魔</span><span color="#7fffff">「渊冰」</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">霜落原地蓄力，刀尖闪光，飞快转身造成<span color="#99ffff">90%</span><span>伤害，若已开盾，则伤害提升，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害。可附魔</span><span color="#7fffff">「渊冰」</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当霜落的生命值<span color="#ffbfbf">低于20%</span><span>时，立即跳起用冰刀下落攻击，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">200%</span><span>伤害，并且附属</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#99ffff">晶寒加护</span><span>，使用</span><span color="#ff9999">火</span><span>破盾最高效，盾破后霜落立即死亡。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
