		<RichText x="1314" y="862" width="433" height="178" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="32" fontWeight="bold" color="#b2d8ff">固有天赋：赴北<br/><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">依据霜落的盾量，其出招方式也有不同，<br/>其分为3个战斗阶段：<br/></span><span fontSize="24" color="#9fe4ff">阶段1：</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">开盾之前；<br/></span><span fontSize="24" color="#9fe4ff">阶段2：</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">开盾之后，盾量</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffbfbf">大于等于40%</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">；<br/></span><span fontSize="24" color="#9fe4ff">阶段3：</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">盾量</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffbfbf">低于等于40%</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">；</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
	</Group>
</Graphic>